{
  "stem": "7358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and-- and if some neighbor of his gets a wind that we are there and they inform to the police, we'll all be slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he suggest that we should go into a area away from his home, perhaps two miles into the woods.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We considered that to be sort of a secluded area in the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went there, and we were waiting there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his wife used to come and bring us food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- the peasants in that area used to go run to pick berries in the woods that time of year.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to use a pail to collect the berries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when it was all done, they would-- it was a tradition-- they would cover it with a white cloth-like to take it home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she put the food in a pail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it appear as if she-- if she was going to collect berries or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she used to bring us the food for about a week or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the farmer came, and he said that it's too danger-- it really was a rather small forest in relation to all the other forests in the area.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he suggested that perhaps he knows that in another forest, quite a distance from here-- from here, there are other Jews hiding.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And maybe if we went into that area, perhaps we would feel safer to be with-- with-- with other people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we realized that he really wanted us to go because he could no longer sustain her coming and bringing us food, and he was afraid for his life.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we thanked him very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we walked during the night mostly and in the evening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did find the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
